          <p class='first-para'>
            I take it from what the noble Lord said that he will not be moving Amendments Nos. 40 to 43 inclusive.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0657P0-04275'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0657P0_20040120_GCR_208' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
